snippet.title: THE FOOD CHALLENGE THAT ROY KEANE ATTEMPTED...IT MADE HIM ANGRY | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at the legendary British institution that is Harry Ramsden's...a fish and chip shop which has been in operation for almost an entire century...

We're here to take on their huge fish 'n chip platter challenge; made famous by Manchester United and Republic of Ireland captain (and perennial grumpy pundit) Roy Keane, in his autobiography, wherein he tells the story of the entire squad preparing for a game against Austria in 1995 by attempting to finish it!

Diners get 30 minutes in which to finish a huge platter of chips, battered fish, deep fried sausages, chicken balls, mushy peas, pickles and an assortment of condiments. Get it down and it's FREE!

snippet.title: Dave Chappelle Delivers Unforgettable Speech & Stands Strong for the People | NAACP Image Awards '25
snippet.description:
Dave Chappelle is recognized as one of the greatest comedians of all time. He is the 2019 recipient of the prestigious Mark Twain Prize for American Humor. Chappelle’s work has earned him more than 30 nominations and awards in television and film for projects that include his groundbreaking sketch comedy television series Chappelle’s Show, comedy specials, and guest appearances on Saturday Night Live. Chappelle has received five Emmy awards, including three for his Netflix comedy specials Sticks & Stones (2020) and Equanimity & The Bird Revelation (2018), and two for hosting Saturday Night Live (2017 and 2021). Chappelle has won six GRAMMY® Awards for Best Comedy Album, winning most recently in 2025 with The Dreamer.

snippet.title: Damon & Marlon Wayans Share Loving, Hilarious Speech at NAACP Image Awards '25 Hall of Fame
snippet.description:
The Wayans family has redefined comedy and entertainment for decades. Led by Keenen Ivory Wayans, creator of In Living Color, they broke barriers in film, TV, and stand-up comedy, launching the careers of stars like Jim Carrey, Jamie Foxx, and Jennifer Lopez. With a fearless approach to storytelling, Keenen and his siblings—Damon, Marlon, Shawn, and Kim—have created iconic works like Scary Movie, White Chicks, and The Wayans Bros. The next generation, including Damon Wayans Jr., is continuing the legacy, with Marlon starring in Respect and Air, and the family gearing up for a Scary Movie reboot in 2026.

snippet.title: Koenigsegg Jesko v Bugatti Chiron Super Sport: DRAG RACE
snippet.description:
We'd like to say a huge thank you to the Al Ain Municipality (https://www.instagram.com/alainmun) and Tilal Swaihan (https://www.instagram.com/tilalswaihan) for providing the amazing drag strip, built to the highest standards to ensure safe racing and car proving away from the public roads.

Thanks, too, goes to Super Cars Majlis (https://www.instagram.com/supercarsmajlis) for inviting its amazing members along and providing the cars you see in our videos.

Also, a massive thanks goes to Ryan Griffiths at Syvecs (https://www.instagram.com/ryansyvecs) for his help in organising these races!
………………………..………………………..………………………..

We’ve just hit 10 million subscribers on YouTube, and we’re celebrating with the one you’ve all been waiting for… Bugatti vs Koenigsegg Carwow drag race! 

Mat and the team have flown out to Dubai to get their hands on these awesome hypercars, and they’re about to go head-to-head as they race over the quarter-mile for the chequered flag. But which will come out on top? Let’s take a closer look at the stats. 

Starting with the Bugatti, it’s the Chiron Super Sport, which comes with an 8-litre quad-turbo W16 that produces 1600hp and 1600Nm of torque. This power is sent to all four wheels via a 7-speed dual-clutch automatic gearbox, and the car weighs 1,995kg. Following several interior & exterior modifications, the car we have here is valued at £5,000,000.

Alongside it, we have the Koenigsegg Jesko Attack. This is powered by a 5-litre twin-turbo V8, and this creates 1280hp and 1000Nm. This power is sent to the rear wheels only via a 9-speed multi-clutch gearbox, and it weighs a whole lot less than the Bugatti, tipping the scales at just 1,420kg! But just like the Chiron Super Sport, it has a price tag of £5,000,000. 

So the Bugatti is well up on power, but it weighs half a tonne more than the Koenigsegg! Could the weight difference prove decisive? There’s only one way to find out for sure… LET’S RACE!
